        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Justice Safety Valve Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes a court to impose a sentence below the mandatory minimum if it determines, after considering certain factors, that the mandatory minimum sentence is greater than necessary. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
